OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy start
OL,6,Fto the evening with isolated showers
OL,7,Fdying out and clear intervals
OL,8,Fdeveloping. Dry overnight with clear
OL,9,Fspells in the west, cloudier with some
OL,10,Flight rain or showers in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy start to the day,
OL,13,Fperhaps some light showers in east but
OL,14,Fcloud breaking up to give long sunny
OL,15,Fperiods through the afternoon. Windy
OL,16,Falong Solway coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
